{
  "text": "There is some freedom as to which CFT with c = \u22122 one should pick. Another possibility [CITATION_1] would be to take the more familiar \u03be\u03b7 ghost system, related to the \u0398 \u03b1 system as follows:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "121010520"
